This repository contains SQL queries demonstrating the use of **Set Operators** in SQL using sample employee, customer, and order tables.

## Tables Used

- CurrentEmployees
- FormerEmployees
- DomesticCustomers
- InternationalCustomers
- OnlineOrders
- StoreOrders

