## UNION

### 1. Display all employee names from current and former employees without duplicates.

```sql
SELECT EmployeeName
FROM CurrentEmployees
UNION
SELECT EmployeeName
FROM FormerEmployees;
```

### 2. Display all departments from both employee tables.

```sql
SELECT Department
FROM CurrentEmployees
UNION
SELECT Department
FROM FormerEmployees;
```

